div_count <- function(n){
  return(sum(n%%(1:n)==0))
}
div_count(10)
## [1] 4

(2) n .

prime_count <- function(n){
    return(sum(sapply(1:n, div_count) == 2))
}
prime_count(10)
## [1] 4
